{"tid":1702798,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"的士遭誤毀 市民即籌維修費","createTime":"2019-11-10T02:26:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T02:37:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e3e6192435c5432978bf831ca1fa2ace332f9562","tid":1702798,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T02:26:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191110/R6Y7WV6GGHW5ZEBGEJTPXBMWUU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191110%2FR6Y7WV6GGHW5ZEBGEJTPXBMWUU%2F&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpsQ0GhOv7yEvjYTsEPvBCF8%3D&h=158c6c06\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191110%2FR6Y7WV6GGHW5ZEBGEJTPXBMWUU%2F&h=dbaeee18\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191110/R6Y7WV6GGHW5ZEBGEJTPXBMWUU/</a><br />\n<br />\n的士遭誤毀 市民即籌維修費<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】旺角昨凌晨有示威者在彌敦道堵路，一輛的士倒車時險撞人群，示威者包圍的士理論，其間一名男子以磚頭扑爆車頭擋風玻璃即逃走，在場人士其後釐清真相，「私了」掟磚男，他被打至頭破血流。在場巿民又發起眾籌，為的士司機分擔數千元維修費。<br />\n<br />\n昨凌晨2時許，旺角彌敦道與亞皆老街交界有大批示威者聚集，一輛空載的士途經，因路障及人群阻路而倒車，險與另一輛的士相撞及撞到市民。在場人士誤以為司機蓄意撞人，一度不滿並拍打車身洩憤，其中一名灰衣男子更以磚頭扑爛的士之擋風玻璃，姓鄭司機頭部亦被擊中輕傷。<br />\n<br />\n擾攘一輪後，示威者確認是誤會一場，有人認為掟磚灰衣男是「鬼」，雙方發生口角，繼而追逐至奶路臣街，灰衣男走避不及被私了，遭人拳打腳踢，頭破血流，義務急救員為其即場治理，最後由救護員送院。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/BK1ILFRX6YRXxUGJCHXNCDWMBmo=/802x502/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/J5DUAIMNEKIWRP5ULJTL7HXXGI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FBK1ILFRX6YRXxUGJCHXNCDWMBmo%3D%2F802x502%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FJ5DUAIMNEKIWRP5ULJTL7HXXGI.gif&h=5179b37a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n姓鄭司機不介意被打爛車窗，並即場點算款項。唐家輝攝<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n司機不介懷<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：性侵傳聞不絕 女生脫口罩控訴<br />\n<br />\n無辜被打爛的士的鄭姓司機，即場獲眾人籌款作為維修費及車租，短短幾分鐘籌得數千元，現鈔放滿膠籃內，另有人私下贈予千多元給他補償。鄭表示，前日下午5時開工，事發前於佐敦接載一名乘客，並於旺角附近落車，駛經上址見阻路於是倒車，豈料引起誤會。對於被打爛車他並不介懷，「唔係好爛，整好就得喇！」昨日無法做生意，「今（昨）日嗰啲冇計，市民都好熱心」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者唐家輝"},{"pid":"781dfca0d74b8e122cedfa148ed010e2f392bfef","tid":1702798,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T02:30:52.000Z","msg":"鶳如果啄爆佢春袋就會好壯觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">千祈唔好啊~</span></span>"},{"pid":"e043bc5aec7b9174986d011d44bbd015c492aa77","tid":1702798,"uid":29514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T02:32:56.000Z","msg":"其實想知被獅個個最後係咪肯定真係鬼？怕獅錯人"},{"pid":"ebafa249c017d7d5c2d033aaedbf21ef726ac9c7","tid":1702798,"uid":298833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T02:36:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d589c924fffbf619fedb4ac3bc21b2bc7abd821","tid":1702798,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e043bc5aec7b9174986d011d44bbd015c492aa77","tid":1702798,"uid":29514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T02:32:56.000Z","msg":"其實想知被獅個個最後係咪肯定真係鬼？怕獅錯人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T02:36:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望唔係手足"},{"pid":"f01e7298e6f487b42f79ddc26bfe15b39dec73b2","tid":1702798,"uid":197121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T02:37:42.000Z","msg":"唔知點解真係可能誤會<br />\n打玻璃可能都係手足"}]}